    "actual_capabilities": [
      "Explains when to create simple, complex, or agent-based skills.",
      "Provides markdown templates for SKILL.md and detailed CLAUDE.md guides.",
      "Defines naming, description, activation, and testing conventions.",
      "Includes workflows for creating new skills and updating existing skills.",
      "Shows how to document agents, parallel work, resources, and command references."
    ],
    "limitations": [
      "It is documentation only and does not generate files automatically.",
      "Template command examples must be reviewed before reuse.",
      "It reflects PAI-specific conventions that may need adaptation.",
      "It does not validate finished skills against marketplace rules."
